Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫和宗朗接吻后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变身为剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.81,0:00:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我愿意去吻她的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说这个处置也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我实在不忍心把失忆的女孩子赶出门外”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这话的是宗朗你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我说的 可…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须承认 十兵卫还算是个很讲道理的武士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 破邪显正之阵对她不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明她也并非邪魔之道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫终究是个危险的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.46,0:00:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得庆幸的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫只要不和宗朗接吻的话 根本人畜无害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 只要你不去吻她就不会有任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身反对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说这个契约对十兵卫以外的武士也起作用的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印掉宗朗的吻就太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就来吻妾身 试试把妾身变成剑姬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你你这个大脑门荡妇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样还称得上是大和抚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有没有羞耻心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笼罩大日本的暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这股威胁依然未见消退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终有一日 这个国家会陷入前所未有的绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那个时候我们需要的究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和抚子的典雅?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女的羞涩?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.69,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有剑姬那强大的力量才能拯救这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是 守卫大日本的剑姬的数量在不断减少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 德川千
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为幕府的公主 你就该有大无畏的气概
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率先尝试与宗朗接吻 看看会有什么结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说 人家也没法去吻宗朗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 毕竟从某种角度上来说这样算人体实验了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,订立契约的仪式是接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻之后的将相会无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而武士成为剑姬之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格也会发生巨大改变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都前所未闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不知道这里面暗藏着多少风险
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德川千
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身也能理解你害怕接吻的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说这个意思啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是说什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了变强而去接吻 总觉得没法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像是背叛自己一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事还是应该和喜欢的人一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着好像你是童男啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 女孩子不可以讲这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样 幸村你又如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾…妾身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是接个吻而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 妾身才不想被你这个童男念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了不要叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑姬是属于幕府的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不允许你们再继续增加来历不明的剑姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是得把你请出这座道场才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生会会竭尽全力 阻止你和宗朗接吻!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等 千姬大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.27,0:05:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翌日早上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 人家还要再吃一碗啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 小幸全都吃掉了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小幸你可真是个贪吃鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 小幸不是离开这里了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来从梦中醒来后又做了一个梦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 辛苦你了 又兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 兵又
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不是做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.10,0:06:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幸还有兵又她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你肯定吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 原来哥哥你早就知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦 一大清早的吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千姬和半藏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以现在让幸村和又兵卫住在别馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幸和兵又要在这里住下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前是这样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万岁!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警告?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫 严禁你跨入宗朗周围半径三米的范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上的事你全都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫做了什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门锁好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,书店的店员没觉得奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.88,0:07:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付钱的时候有用经济类书籍挡住这摞书的上面和下面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有拿好收据
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明确摆出一副“这些书都是用于工作!”的样子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一本了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻 真是令人生畏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.74,0:07:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是与人接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其种类也可细分为French kiss  Deep kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28}Bird kiss  Pressure kiss  Rhythm kiss  Cocktail kiss  Throat kiss  Searching kiss  Sky-love-hurricane kiss{\r}等等各种各样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好险…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来妾身当时没有立刻吻他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择暂时撤退是正确的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然妾身明白事先了解相关知识是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没想到居然如此博大精深…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就普通地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通地去吻他不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说说看 什么是普通的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 普通地去吻啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是普通 什么是不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是全凭个人主观而形成的不确定感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要谈普通的话 首先就应该界定它的判定标准才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您很紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么一点点啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们都没有什么动静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定对公主大人铜墙铁壁般的防御望而生畏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.18,0:08:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻并不是能那么轻易做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 兵又
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我的伤已经全好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在生我的气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经和我们道了很多次歉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村大人也没有生你的气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幸和哥哥接吻后会变得更强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌其他的女性和宗朗接吻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…但是十兵卫不可以说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为十兵卫和哥哥接吻后…伤害了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起十兵卫 和其他女性接吻的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥肯定会高兴得多…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动摇啊 妾身的心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只不过是个单纯的手段而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是身体的一部份瞬间接触而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你上当了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德川千
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜呀 你这半夜偷腥的大脑门荡妇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然算计我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:10:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“不要动摇啊 妾身的心”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“这只不过是个单纯的手段而已”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么为了大日本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.72,0:11:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你好意思对千那么冠冕堂皇地说教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不要误会喔…妾身只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“只是身体的一部份…”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“…瞬间接触而已”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种小豆丁想接吻 还早了三年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少等你每天喝牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸围长了三厘米之后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身的纯情 这一刻死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.68,0:11:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 说什么妾身也要和宗朗接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒要瞧瞧看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻作战 其一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻作战 其二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻作战 其三
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻作战 其四
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻作战 其五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻作战 其六
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中场休息…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幸 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有我帮得上忙的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妾身和学生会之间的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要其他人插手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身居然如此毫无考量就一味地莽撞行动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是像小幸这样的天才要接吻也很难喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都是为了让德川千疏忽大意的计策而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来才是重头戏!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为看你好像吃了不少苦头…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身还没潦倒到需要敌人来关心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可哥哥不是敌人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.03,0:13:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.39,0:13:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要认真地刷牙喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对妾身最基本的礼貌…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样的话应该不会留下疤痕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身好歹也是一介武士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有一两个疤痕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你首先是一个女孩子 其次才是武士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比脸上没有疤痕更重要的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要更加爱惜自己才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再把事情弄得更复杂了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复杂?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说…妾身…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…会困扰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身到底在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就像个傻子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聪明反被聪明误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来妾身只得承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似 似乎…妾身喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸…村?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 公主大人什么时候准许你单独行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你多体谅一下千姬大人的苦心再行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:15:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村大人 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幸 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道这样阻挠别人也只是无济于事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像个傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.76,0:15:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏永远都会追随着公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事请尽管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半藏在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这茶叶是哪儿产的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道…这是道场里原本就有的茶叶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给千喝这种廉价货 想要千的命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然听从千的任何命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还不快把这些茶叶都给千吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算能一个人自在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到那个份上 幸村也该收手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后得好好向千姬和半藏道歉才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.66,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫只不过是协助我完成计划而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.73,0:16:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若要处罚的话 罚我一个人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这件事暂且不谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十兵卫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过你讨厌宗朗和其他的女性接吻的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果是小幸的话 没问题喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小幸和十兵卫一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级喜欢哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就此告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight 小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该…该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸 幸 幸 幸村!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底都在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是挂了“入浴中”的牌子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 算了 我这就出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你闭上眼睛10秒钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望妾身闭上眼睛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得…那个 哪一种比较可爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接吻时是女生是闭着眼睛好 还是睁开眼睛好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之现在请等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是武士间最起码的尊重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有喝太多的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉 幸村大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然使出…这么下三滥的手段…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千姬大人 请你冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德川流薙刀术奥义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炎闪破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的德川千
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙下手都不知道轻重的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要淹死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来只是昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉心脏紧张得快要跳出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.58,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…变成剑姬了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和妾身所想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到没 德川千
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身作为剑姬的绚丽身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什么都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能糟蹋妾身的盛装登场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.83,0:19:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该死的雾气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你都干了些什么啊 笨蛋幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分喔 小幸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道没办法控制自己的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去事情会大条的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧 宗朗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身并没打算使力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…而且…虽说是场意外 不过对不起!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.68,0:20:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是跟你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翌日早上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你打算无视这个惨状吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为哥哥会努力把这些全都恢复原状的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬让我收拾这烂摊子也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这个面具是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你反省好那个吻之前都不许摘下来!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉今天也会有好事情发生喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.08,0:21:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶叶…好好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百花缭乱 SAMURAI GIRLS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 来订立契约吧
